接口 InstanceMethodAdvice

    public interface InstanceMethodAdvice

    Instance method advice.

    • 方法详细资料

      • beforeMethod

        default void beforeMethod​(TargetAdviceObject target,
                          Method method,
                          Object[] args,
                          String pluginType)
        Intercept the target method and weave the method before origin method. It will invoke before the origin calling.
        参数:
        target - the target object
        method - the target method
        args - all method arguments
        pluginType - plugin type

      • afterMethod

        default void afterMethod​(TargetAdviceObject target,
                         Method method,
                         Object[] args,
                         Object result,
                         String pluginType)
        Intercept the target method and weave the method after origin method. It will invoke after the origin calling
        参数:
        target - the target object
        method - the target method
        args - all method arguments
        result - original call result
        pluginType - plugin type

      • onThrowing

        default void onThrowing​(TargetAdviceObject target,
                        Method method,
                        Object[] args,
                        Throwable throwable,
                        String pluginType)
        Weaving the method after origin method throwing.
        参数:
        target - the target object
        method - the target method
        args - all method arguments
        throwable - exception from target method
        pluginType - plugin type
